quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,154,"Kandi ntimukavuge ko abishwe baguye mu rugamba rwo guharanira inzira ya Allah bapfuye, ahubwo ni bazima <sup>1</sup> nyamara mwe ntimubyiyumvisha.","[1] Ubuzima buvugwa aha ni ubuzima bwa Roho y’uwapfuye mu nzira ya Allah, iyo roho ikomeza kubaho mu byishimo."
  2,155,"Rwose tuzabagerageza dukoresheje kubateza ubwoba, inzara, kugabanuka kw’imitungo, gupfusha abantu no kurumbya imyaka. Ngaho ha inkuru nziza abihangana.",""
  2,156,"Ba bandi igihe bahuye n’ibyago bavuga bati “Mu by’ukuri, turi aba Allah kandi iwe ni ho tuzasubira.”",""
  2,157,"Abo bafite imigisha, impuhwe ndetse n’imbabazi bituruka kwa Nyagasani wabo, kandi ni na bo bayobotse.",""
  2,158,"Mu by’ukuri (imisozi ya) Swafa na Maruwa<sup>1</sup> ni bimwe mu bimenyetso bya Allah. Bityo uzakora umutambagiro mutagatifu wa Hija<sup>2</sup> cyangwa Umura<sup>3</sup> kuri iyo nzu (Al Kabat), nta cyo bitwaye kuri we kuyitambagira yombi (iyo misozi ya Swafa na Maruwa). N’uzakora ibyiza ku bushake bwe (amenye ko) Allah ari Ushima, Umumenyi uhebuje.","[1] Swafa na Maruwa: Ni imisozi ibiri yegeranye n’umusigiti mutagatifu wa Maka. \n[2] Hija: Ni umutambagiro mutagatifu ku ngoro (Al Kaabat) ya Allah iri i Maka, ukahakora ibikorwa n’amagambo runaka hagamijwe kwiyegereza Allah mu gihe cyagenwe. \n[3] Umurat: Ni ugusura ingoro ya Al Kaaba mu gihe icyo ari cyo cyose ukora ibikorwa byagenwe byo kwiyegereza Allah."
  2,159,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi bahisha ibimenyetso bigaragara ndetse n’umuyoboro twahishuye, nyuma y’uko tubigaragarije abantu mu gitabo, abo Allah arabavuma ndetse n’abavuma bose bakabasabira imivumo.",""
  2,160,"Uretse abicujije bagakora ibikorwa byiza kandi bakagaragaza (ibyo bari barahishe); abo ni bo nakirira ukwicuza kwabo. Ni Nanjye Uwakira ukwicuza, Nyirimbabazi.",""
  2,161,"Mu by’ukuri, abahakanye bakanapfa ari abahakanyi, abo umuvumo wa Allah ubariho, uw’abamalayika, ndetse n’uw’abantu bose.",""
  2,162,"Bazawubamo ubuziraherezo, ntibazoroherezwa ibihano ndetse nta n’ubwo bazahabwa agahenge.",""
  2,163,"Kandi Imana yanyu ni Imana imwe, nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa uretse yo, Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi.",""
